title: Cafe Louise - Ramat Aviv
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Israeli, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Trendy cafe with several locations. Vegan, vegetarian, and gluten-free items are marked on the menu. Offers at least 2 vegan items in each category, such as mains, huge salads, pasta, and breakfast. Casual, family friendly.
